{"tid":1765330,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"反曼入","createTime":"2019-12-01T19:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T14:36:42.000Z","uid":42246,"like":40,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6e80b1aa641d81db56981b7290c27e1043285f38","tid":1765330,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T19:02:24.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺依隊曼聯係有史以來最撚垃圾？<br />\n睇左咁耐波 除左自己隊波<br />\n身為反曼 最留意就係曼聯<br />\n<br />\n嘩依家隊野真係垃圾到反艇<br />\n理性反曼都唔覺得佢地會輸比Google隊啦<br />\n點知都輸<br />\n季初6場8分 我以為曼聯想激多次費sir爆血管<br />\n<br />\n最恐怖係影響埋我地反曼 輸到連曼都唔想反<br />\n輸波輸到食生菜咁 同今年英超冠軍一定係利咁<br />\n冇曬意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15083a8aa28d276c962e90a617c4275e0ccf3d8","tid":1765330,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T19:08:47.000Z","msg":"又想呃正評？<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"1dff676031d0e02fbe42cb97d2f6a9dacb1453b8","tid":1765330,"uid":42246,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b15083a8aa28d276c962e90a617c4275e0ccf3d8","tid":1765330,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T19:08:47.000Z","msg":"又想呃正評？<br />\n拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T19:21:39.000Z","msg":"想睇下反曼認唔認同<br />\n<br />\n依個世界上得兩種人最了解曼<br />\n一是死曼狗<br />\n二是反曼"},{"pid":"2426de78e970975681aefcba00e02431953aa9ae","tid":1765330,"uid":306576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T19:22:22.000Z","msg":"廢蟃"},{"pid":"2f21bcb55b73cc211a6270cf9831337be241e551","tid":1765330,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T20:51:16.000Z","msg":"反父入"},{"pid":"62917b79688d210eba1b5676bd50bf512eafbea7","tid":1765330,"uid":243526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f21bcb55b73cc211a6270cf9831337be241e551","tid":1765330,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T20:51:16.000